" (escape from the evil paranthesis, braces and brackets afterwards with ^L)
" :inoremap ( ()<ESC>:let leavechar=")"<CR>i
" :inoremap { {}<ESC>:let leavechar="}"<CR>i
" :inoremap [ []<ESC>:let leavechar="]"<CR>i

":imap <C-l> <ESC>:exec "normal f" . leavechar<CR>a

